<html>
  <head>
    <title>Dockerized NAS - services</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>
      Dockerized Services
    </h1>
    <p>
      Please find all services running on this machine below.
    </p>
    <hr />

      <h2>sickbeard</h2>
      <p>
        The sickbeard pvr application for tv shoes
      </p>
      <p>
        Used to search for tv shows and series which then will be automatically downloaded
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="http://{{ansible_default_ipv4.address}}:8081">
          Link to sickbeard
        </a>
      </p>

      <h2>couchpotato</h2>
      <p>
        The couchpotato pvr application for movies
      </p>
      <p>
        Search for movies and automatically download them when they become available
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="http://{{ansible_default_ipv4.address}}:5050">
          Link to couchpotato
        </a>
      </p>

      <h2>sabnzbd</h2>
      <p>
        The full auto newsreader
      </p>
      <p>
        Used to download the movies and tv shows found by couchpotato and sickbeard
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="http://{{ansible_default_ipv4.address}}:8085">
          Link to sabnzbd
        </a>
      </p>

      <h2>plex</h2>
      <p>
        The plex media server
      </p>
      <p>
        Used to watch downloaded movies, series and listen to audiobooks and music.
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="http://{{ansible_default_ipv4.address}}:32400/web">
          Link to plex
        </a>
      </p>

      <h2>OpenVPN Access Server</h2>
      <p>
        The OpenVPN Access Server
      </p>
      <p>
        Securely connect to the homework over OpenVPN
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="http://{{ansible_default_ipv4.address}}:943">
          Link to OpenVPN
        </a>
      </p>

      <h2>Fedora Cockpit (no docker container)</h2>
      <p>
        The server cockpit
      </p>
      <p>
        Used for basic server administration
      </p>
      <p>
        <a href="http://{{ansible_default_ipv4.address}}:9090">
          Link to Cockpit
        </a>
      </p>

      </body>
</html>
